%section.features
  .row
    .large-6.columns.text-center
      %h2.underline Increase Club Profits
      %p Using Tap you can charge a service fee to the performers and/or charge a percentage of every transaction. You control the tipping platform and can monetize. You can also collect tips for the DJ, bartenders or even pieces of art on the wall. Big tippers can tip everything they like. They will also be encouraged to tip more to get to the top of the ‘top tippers’ leaderboard.
    .large-6.columns.text-center
      %h2.underline Capture More Data
      %p Who are your big tippers? Reward them more and get them to come back more often. Who are the favorite performers? Who are your best bartenders? Tap captures the most valuable data for your club—what your customers like. That Real-time Data helps you run your business better.
%section.about
  .row.text-center
    .large-3.columns
      %i.fa.fa-lock.fa-4
      %h4 A More Secure Solution
      %p
        Tap keeps you in control of your cash! Our solution keeps it localized to one secure location, and frees your performers (and staff)
        from keeping track of cash.
    .large-3.columns
      %i.fa.fa-money.fa-4
      %h4 Flexible Payments
      %p
        Continue to process credit cards and collect cash, using tap to capture the distribution of the cash and credit card charges and pay out your
        contractors, performers, and staff at the end of the night.
    .large-3.columns
      %i.fa.fa-puzzle-piece.fa-4
      %h4 Fully Customized
      %p
        The app is built to be fully customized as a natural extension of your club's technology. Your logo goes in the app and on the leaderboard.
        Customized for your venue, with many opportunities for marketing your special events and promotions.
    .large-3.columns
      %i.fa.fa-line-chart.fa-4
      %h4 Reporting and Analytics
      %p
        Keep regulators and auditors off your back with software designed to be fully compliant with federal, state, and local standards.
        Our real-time monitoring and reporting simplifies the nightly payout process, and helps you find and fix inefficiency <strong>before</strong> it costs you money.
